PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FAlmost 6,000 households missed out on
OL,8,Frecycling collections on the first day
OL,9,Fof a new system, prompting an apology
OL,10,Ffrom Stockton Council.
OL,12,FA leading councillor said they were
OL,13,Fovercoming "teething problems", while
OL,14,Fa local MP criticised the system as
OL,15,F"chaos" after thousands of residents
OL,16,Fdid not have their recycling collected
OL,17,Fon Tuesday 31 March, the Local
OL,18,FDemocracy Reporting Service reports.
OL,26,@uD@LOUuD@^O]wD@AOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FIt marked the start of a new system
OL,8,Fwhere food waste now goes into
OL,9,Fcaddies, while plastics, tins, cartons
OL,10,Fgo into blue bags, cardboard and paper
OL,11,Finto white bags and glass and
OL,12,Fbatteries into a blue box, all
OL,13,Fcollected weekly. General waste from
OL,14,Ftraditional bins and garden waste are
OL,15,Fnow collected fortnightly.
OL,17,FThe authority has said waste crews
OL,18,Fwill work on Saturday (4 April) to
OL,19,Fcatch up on the missed collections.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FStockton Council put out a statement
OL,8,Fon Tuesday afternoon saying: "We are
OL,9,Faware that some residents have not had
OL,10,Ftheir recycling collected today (March
OL,11,F31) as planned. Crews have been
OL,12,Fworking to get through as many
OL,13,Fproperties as they can but have now
OL,14,Fhad to stop due to drivers working the
OL,15,Fmaximum hours they are legally
OL,16,Fpermitted.
OL,26,@pD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"The delays to collections has been
OL,8,Fcaused by issues with unloading the
OL,9,Fwagons and we are very sorry for the
OL,10,Finconvenience. If your recycling was
OL,11,Fdue to be collected today and has not
OL,12,Fbeen collected, crews will be doing a
OL,13,Fcatch-up collection on Saturday (April
OL,14,F4).
OL,16,F"Collections will continue as normal
OL,17,Ftomorrow, Thursday and Friday as the
OL,18,Fissues with unloading the wagons have
OL,19,Fnow been resolved. Once again we are
OL,20,Fvery sorry for any inconvenience and
OL,21,Fthank you for your patience."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FStockton West Conservative MP Matt
OL,8,FVickers said he had heard reports of
OL,9,Fseveral vehicles "out of action on the
OL,10,Fvery first day" and residents saying
OL,11,Ftheir carefully separated waste was
OL,12,Fbeing mixed together in collection
OL,13,Fwagons.
OL,15,FHe has written to Mike Greene, the
OL,16,Fchief executive of the Labour-led
OL,17,Fcouncil, to find out what the council
OL,18,Fwould do to remedy the situation, and
OL,19,Fhas launched a survey to gather views
OL,20,Fon the new system.
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FMr Vickers said: "Labour's new waste
OL,8,Fand recycling scheme is utter chaos.
OL,9,FThere have been numerous reports of
OL,10,Fresidents doing the right thing `
OL,11,Ftaking the time to sort their waste `
OL,12,Fonly to see it all mixed up and thrown
OL,13,Finto the same wagon. That makes a sham
OL,14,Fof the entire process.
OL,16,F"This isn't the fault of our
OL,17,Fhardworking bin men. They are doing a
OL,18,Ftough job. It is the result of a
OL,19,Fridiculous new scheme introduced by
OL,20,FStockton Labour.
OL,26,@oD@ROUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"Expecting people to juggle six
OL,8,Fdifferent bins while scrapping weekly
OL,9,Fcollections is complete madness.
OL,10,FHaving warned about the consequences
OL,11,Fwhen the council proposed this I have
OL,12,Fwritten to the chief executive of the
OL,13,Fcouncil to think again about their
OL,14,Fapproach. It simply isn't working for
OL,15,Flocal residents or the bin men who
OL,16,Fwork hard day in, day out."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FThe food waste collection was brought
OL,8,Fin nationally by law. The swap to
OL,9,Fweekly recycling and fortnightly non-
OL,10,Frecycled waste collections was decided
OL,11,Fby the council following the unanimous
OL,12,Frecommendation of a cross-party
OL,13,Fcommittee, including Conservative
OL,14,Fmembers, to improve the town's
OL,15,Frecycling rate, which had been the
OL,16,Flowest on Teesside and one of the
OL,17,Flowest nationally.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FCllr Nigel Cooke, cabinet member for
OL,8,Fenvironment, leisure and culture,
OL,9,Frepeated the apology to residents who
OL,10,Fdid not get their recycling collected.
OL,11,FBut he said he believed residents were
OL,12,Fsupportive of the "momentous change"
OL,13,Fwhich affected everyone.
OL,15,FHe said: "We'll be going back to those
OL,16,Fhouses on Saturday morning. If we'd
OL,17,Fstarted off today there'd have been a
OL,18,Fknock-on effect.
OL,26,@tD@SOUtD@dO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"With a massive change like this, we
OL,8,Falways expected some teething
OL,9,Fproblems. This has been the biggest
OL,10,Fchange that I've been associated with
OL,11,Fduring my time on the council since
OL,12,F2011."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FHe said the "magnificent" Care For
OL,8,FYour Area team had worked hard to
OL,9,Fprepare for the changes and get used
OL,10,Fto new vehicles and systems, adding:
OL,11,F"We did everything we could pro-
OL,12,Factively to try and get things in
OL,13,Fplace, but there was inevitably going
OL,14,Fto be a few bumps in the road. You
OL,15,Fcan't expect things to work perfectly
OL,16,Fon day one.
OL,18,F"There was a lot of learning
OL,19,Fyesterday. I'm confident we'll get
OL,20,Fthis to where we need it to be within
OL,21,Fthe next few days.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@YO]sD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"Some of the things weren't working as
OL,8,Fwe expected them to. There was a lot
OL,9,Fof thinking on the ground. Until you
OL,10,Factually go live you don't know what
OL,11,Fyou're up against.
OL,13,F"There was an increased demand. There
OL,14,Fwas a lot of recycling to collect.
OL,15,FThey've had the new bags for a couple
OL,16,Fof weeks, they've probably stored
OL,17,Fquite a lot of material. That'll
OL,18,Fsettle down."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FHe encouraged people who did not have
OL,8,Fblue boxes or bags to contact the
OL,9,Fcouncil, saying: "We'll be making sure
OL,10,Fthey get everything."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FIn response to Mr Vickers' criticisms,
OL,8,FCllr Nigel Cooke said: "We are
OL,9,Fenacting changes brought about by the
OL,10,Flast Conservative government. We
OL,11,Factually support them, I believe in
OL,12,Frecycling."
OL,14,FHe said they had seen a "massive
OL,15,Fuptake" in people wanting to recycle
OL,16,Fin the last few days, with "massive
OL,17,Fqueues" to get white bags and blue
OL,18,Fboxes, adding: "Those receptacles will
OL,19,Fbe available at libraries. They're
OL,20,Fflying out of the door as soon as they
OL,21,Fcome in.
OL,26,@pD@XOUtD@KO]vD@YOUwD@GO]xD@\OUyD@GO]zD@
OL,26,APOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"This tells me that people are
OL,8,Fengaging, they want to recycle and
OL,9,Fit's just going to take a few days for
OL,10,Fpeople to get used to these changes."
OL,12,FAsked about reports of separated types
OL,13,Fof recycling being mixed and put into
OL,14,Fthe same wagon, he said: "We did order
OL,15,Fa fleet of new vehicles. We're still
OL,16,Fwaiting for some of those vehicles to
OL,17,Fcome.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@eO]vD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"So there were many of the vehicles
OL,8,Fout on the road yesterday. There were
OL,9,Fa few technical faults which were
OL,10,Fovercome very quickly.
OL,12,F"We also had to supplement this with
OL,13,Fother vehicles including flat back
OL,14,Fwagons. At the end of the day, that
OL,15,Frecycling will be presented to the
OL,16,Frecycling company as it should be.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"We've been pulling out the stops to
OL,8,Fmake sure everything was collected.
OL,9,FClearly there were those few hiccups.
OL,10,FI'm reliably informed that not one
OL,11,Fgreen bin was missed."
OL,13,FHe denied Mr Vickers' assertions that
OL,14,Fbin men were "forced to work late into
OL,15,Fthe night to complete their rounds",
OL,16,Fsaying they worked as long as they
OL,17,Flegally could: "They can't drive
OL,18,Fbeyond a certain amount of time. The
OL,19,Fhealth and safety of all of our staff
OL,20,Fis paramount.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@VO]vD@NOUwD@cO]yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1775426989
OL,3,CNearly 6,000 household recycling
OL,4,Ccollections missed on first day of new
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"We called operations to a halt
OL,8,Fyesterday because we didn't want
OL,9,Fdrivers to exceed those legal limits,
OL,10,Fand that was the right decision. They
OL,11,Fworked hard all day yesterday."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G18/18
